{"productOptionsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p class=\"text-neutral-600\">Use this section for <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">ordering rules</strong>: style number, price band, minimums, and stated production time from the supplier catalog. Final invoice may reflect decoration, proofs, rush, or freight.</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Field</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Value</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Style #</td><td class=\"py-2 font-mono text-neutral-900\">BX-060601-SQR</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">List price range</td><td class=\"py-2\">$42.60 – $49.25 USD</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Minimum quantity</td><td class=\"py-2\">12</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Stated production time</td><td class=\"py-2\">15 days</td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Quantity pricing (USD)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-2\">Price per unit at each order-quantity break (from the live product page).</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Quantity</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Price (each)</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">12</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$49.25 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">25</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$46.75 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">50</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$44.75 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">100</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$43.92 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">250</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$42.60 each</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Catalog highlights</h4><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[13px] leading-snug\"><li>Made in USA</li><li>Box will accommodate a medallion up to 4.50&quot; in diameter</li><li>Laser engrave or digital print</li><li>7 different flocking colors to choose from </li><li>12 different wood finishes to choose from</li></ul>\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mb-2\">Patch options (supplier)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-3\">Options and add-ons from the live Distributor Central product page for this SKU. Pricing may change; confirm on your quote.</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50/30\">\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Inlaid Flocking Color</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">This pressure sensitive adhesive (PSA) flocking is applied to the interior flat bottom and/or top of the box.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">windsor navy blue flock</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Navy Blue</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Similar to PMS 539 C.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">francis med blu flock</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Medium Blue</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Similar to PMS 540 C.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">platinum grey flock</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Grey</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Similar to PMS 402 C</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">bgndy flock</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Burgundy</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Similar to PMS 505 C</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">sherwood green flock</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Green</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Similar to PMS 343 C</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">red flame flock</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Red</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Similar to PMS 186 C</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">bk</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Black</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Velvet Covered Foam Insert</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Custom cut foam inserts are available for all of our boxes.  We can design, program and cut the foam inserts to safely hold and display any item you have to put into the box.\r\n\r\nThe velveteen top covering on the foam is plush, attractive and available in a wide selection of colors. The design and programming is provided free with your order and all you pay is a foam cutter set up fee each time you run the job.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">persian melon 848 velveteen</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Bright Red</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Similar to PMS 185 C</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">emerald green 716 velveteen</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Emerald Green</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Similar to PMS 348 C</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">seagull grey 87 velveteen</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Grey</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Similar to PMS 423 C</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">blue flame 616 velveteen</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Navy Blue</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Similar to PMS 296 C</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">dior red 183 velveteen</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Burgundy</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Similar to PMS 195 C</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">bk</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Black</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Wood / Finish</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/F/1/F1EB48B95E8D7CB21CA793E1535EB12A.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">m</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Maple</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/B/0/B04B11D5D8EABDED8E462D26B2C1E49D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">hm</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Honey Maple</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/E/0/E0B36A997179DAD81E732A0EA8853B6C.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">nc</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Natural Cherry</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/A/B/ABA245DC9F2AB4268162FBB621498AF9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">r</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Rosewood</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/9/7/97FE9BA54B3127E4AB40DDC8636DF76D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">drm</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Dark Red Mahogany</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/B/F/BFF5509C57BD3ED33FBF5B87575CD256.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">e</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Espresso</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/B/3/B33E69A89B2E0B5E8E574B6457614478.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">w</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Walnut</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/C/D/CDF537F42531707ADD6C16F7769C9D01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">dw</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Dark Walnut</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/9/8/9868B70620DB61EEA355034A833E1DD0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">b</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Buckeye</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/9/8/98A3090494A4F39EEABB8A91183FAD54.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">sg</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Storm Gray</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/1/5/156EDEC31CC30D4A63BBF05BCDAE6489.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">bm</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Brown Mahogany</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/A/C/AC554AED01408F12A4CA4216F04E8855.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">bs</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Black Stain</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">wl</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">White Lacquer</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Add 15% to product price for a white lacquer finish.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/E/4/E4BDC3C73C851BC3A163B3A2764E27C1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">bl</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Black Lacquer</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Add 15% to product price for a black lacquer finish.</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Laser Engraving (add'l location or size)</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">The listed product price includes a one position laser engraving up to the size stated (If it shows no setup, the price does not include decoration.)  Additional positions and/or sizes may be added for the prices shown.\r\n\r\nLaser Set up policy:\texact repeat within 6 mo N/C; within 1-2 years 50%</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Laser Engrave Run</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Laser Engrave Run Charge</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">$2.00 (G) up to 4 sq. in.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Laser Engrave Charge +size</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Laser Engrave Run Charge +size</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">$.40 (G) per square inch after 4 sq. in.</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Personalization</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Individual names, initials, monograms or variable data can be directly lasered or digitally printed onto most of our products.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">P-1</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">First line or name personalized</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$5.50 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">P-2</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Additional lines personalized</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$4.50 per line</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Less Than Minimum</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">The minimum quantity of any standard inventory item is limited to one half of the first quantity listed for that item on our website or catalog. Please use the first quantity price as listed in the catalog and add $ 35.00 (G) for blank merchandise and $ 70.00 (G) for decorated merchandise. Setup discounts on repeat orders do not apply to less than minimum purchases.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">LTM-B</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Blank Less Than Minimum</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$35.00 per order</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">LTM-D</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Decorated Less Than Minimum</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$70.00 per order</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Proofs</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Proofs are available on request.  To see your artwork at the actual size and location as it will appear on your finished order, request a paper or digital proof. First digital proof is free with all orders; all additional proofs are $ 7.00.\r\nTo see the actual product with your artwork on it as it will be completed, request a sample proof ($ 60.00 per product plus cost of the item - 7 WD or less after receipt of artwork approval); unless the product has a die cast component, then it is $ 95.00 plus product cost and 12 working days after artwork approval.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Paper</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Paper Proof</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">One proof is provided with each order free of charge.  There is a charge for any subsequent proofs or changes.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$7.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Sample</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Sample Proof</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">An actual piece as you have ordered.  7 working days after receipt of order and artwork approval.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$70.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Sample, dc</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Sample Proof, die cast</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">An actual piece, die casted as you have ordered.  12 working days after receipt of order and artwork approval.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$95.00 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — Medallion Box, 6.13 x 6.13 x 1.50&quot;. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">BX-060601-SQR</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>15 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">12</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}